{"tid":33073,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 論牌面李嘉欣贏定洪欣件西女人贏？","createTime":"2016-12-10T14:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T15:04:31.000Z","uid":53178,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d67e457021c7b18b64db68992c83d25c86dfc2f2","tid":33073,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:47:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大美人李嘉欣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n西女人洪欣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>講樣</strong> <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>李嘉欣 完勝</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2015/06/28/1362118_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2015%2F06%2F28%2F1362118_3.jpg&h=6bc7a5be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ycdtb.dayoo.com/images/2007-04/06/1175973475953070406a24003_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fycdtb.dayoo.com%2Fimages%2F2007-04%2F06%2F1175973475953070406a24003_b.jpg&h=6912f593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>講感情路</strong> <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>李嘉欣 再完勝</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大劉生命中重要嘅人，2006年6月20日生日，獲大劉以The one匿稱，豪擲報紙全版廣告賀壽。分手後，大劉仍然將華置旗下廣場命名The One。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20060621/Article_ent/21ec1p105.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20060621%2FArticle_ent%2F21ec1p105.jpg&h=8321e8a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cfcdn1.azsg.opensnap.com/stickers-resize/trending_100000224-sx.jpg?20160128043000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfcdn1.azsg.opensnap.com%2Fstickers-resize%2Ftrending_100000224-sx.jpg%3F20160128043000&h=008b101a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李嘉欣06年隨即搭上富商許晉亨，2008年結婚，11年生埋仔仔。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.qilook.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/ttps2.buzzhand.netuploadsdde93815714557871873782.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.qilook.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2Fttps2.buzzhand.netuploadsdde93815714557871873782.jpg&h=232b5835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於西女人洪欣<br />\n最為人熟悉係同過外貌酷似ET嘅死窮鬼莫少聰一齊。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.people.com.cn/mediafile/pic/20110729/1/15003858985541692825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.people.com.cn%2Fmediafile%2Fpic%2F20110729%2F1%2F15003858985541692825.jpg&h=a06cd0db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.telegraph.co.uk/multimedia/archive/01474/et_1474485b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.telegraph.co.uk%2Fmultimedia%2Farchive%2F01474%2Fet_1474485b.jpg&h=1f9da1cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年洪欣仲要未婚生咗仔仔莫鎬廉，不過親生老竇唔認帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，近年洪欣改嫁死窮鬼張丹峰，而個野仔就索性跟後父姓，改名張浩鋒。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.tianya999.com/uploads/allimg/130822/2291-130R2102349.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tianya999.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F130822%2F2291-130R2102349.jpg&h=2b28abed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>講仔仔</strong> <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>李嘉欣 再再再完勝</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n許建彤：含住金鎖匙出世，衣食無憂<br />\n張浩鋒：同後父張丹峰拍住上，拍內地嘅電視劇《致青春》，做張丹峰嘅童年版，入娛樂圈步老母西女人洪欣後麈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大美人李嘉欣 完勝<br />\n正評 上一頁</strong></span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3041a9d33f8ab42dc79897c739631f8729559303","tid":33073,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f455xMD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff455xMD.jpg&h=5442bc9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bbe01cb8f76a1d7463b44fe195b846bae9d39ff","tid":33073,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f455xMD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff455xMD.jpg&h=5442bc9f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大陸雞洪欣痴埋大陸男人度<br />\nd圖得大陸報紙先有，有乜出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}